dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v2.bswmoduletemplate.bswbehavior

Interface IBswServiceDependency

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity

    public interface IBswServiceDependency
extends IEntity
    IBswServiceDependency: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    Specialization of ServiceDependency in the context of an BswInternalBehavior. It allows to associate BswModuleEntries and data defined for a BSW module or cluster to a given ServiceNeeds element.
